Zenigen is a nutritional supplement company with an unmatched passion for each and every potent blend we create. Our very first supplement, Zenigen:Focus, came from a question, "Is there a way to expand the brain's potential?" The subsequent supplements we've crafted came from similar questions appropriate for their own category. Our journey started in 2013 when we searched for a supplement to boost our mood, motivation, memory, focus, and concentration. We did not consider those things too much to ask for, however we were surprised that no supplements we tried offered all of those benefits.

That [lack of] discovery initiated our own personal testing. Every day we'd try a new blend of ingredients (usually in the form of bulk powder) and report our findings to each other - both the positive and negative - until, months later, we found a blend that caused us to say, "Yes, this does just what we were hoping for!" Thus, Zenigen (and Zenigen:Focus) was born. There were still many months of A/B testing, minor modifications, and third-party opinions before we finalized the blend to the point it could not get any better.

ABOUT COLORADO SURGICAL CENTER & HAIR INSTITUTE

DENVER HAIR TRANSPLANT CENTER
For more than two and a half decades, the Denver hair transplant experts at Colorado Surgical Center & Hair Institute have assisted thousands of clients restore their scalp and facial hair. Even though we are internationally known for our work on individuals in the entertainment industry, our staff can help nearly anyone restore their hair using various hair transplant techniques. We offer high quality hair transplant services at affordable prices, visit our "Pricing" page. Our goal is for clients to visit our office, receive the hair transplant that is most beneficial for them, and get their hair back for life.

SERVICES
We offer a wide variety of hair transplant services, including:
Follicular Unit Extraction
Natural Follicular Hair Grafting
Trichophytic Donor Closure Technique
Eyebrow Reconstruction
Facial Hair Reconstruction
Hair Transplant Center in Denver

Our advance techniques restore fullness and density of a person's natural hair, and by adapting the use of the dissecting microscope, we can create incredibly small hair grafts that can still retain the natural characteristics of hair growth. Utilizing a dissecting microscope has many other advantages, as well, such as:

Thousands of growing hair follicles can be microsurgically added to thinning or bald areas
Precise follicle-by-follicle microscopic dissection-grafting
New follicular unit grafting an create an undetectable, soft hairline
Very little or no downtime after surgery
Increased hair coverage
Newly transplanted hair is genetically programmed to continue growing, meaning the hair will continue to grow over a client's lifetime
Hair looks completely natural that only you know it is transplanted
Highly affordable. We offer 100% interest-free financing for up to 18 months
CONTACT US TODAY TO SCHEDULE AN APPOINTMENT!

If you wish to learn how we can help you restore your hair and confidence, please contact our office at (303) 569-8237 or (888) 720-8575. We also offer free consultations via our website, as well as travel credit for those who wish to undergo hair transplants but live out of state. Colorado Surgical Center & Hair Institute is one of the best hair restoration institutes in the western United States. Please call our office to schedule an appointment with one of our hair transplant experts today! We serve clients all across the country!
